data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living with this amazing 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom townhouse, situated just a stone's throw away from the electrifying Las Vegas Strip. Boasting a captivating open floorplan, this residence welcomes you with an elegant electric fireplace, while downstairs, sleek tile flooring enhances the ambiance. Upstairs, plush carpeting invites you to unwind in style. The kitchen dazzles with granite countertops, and the primary bedroom offers a private sanctuary, complete with a balcony. Outside, a private courtyard and patio area provide the perfect backdrop for outdoor gatherings. This oasis is nestled within a gated community that offers enticing amenities including a sparkling community pool and tennis courts. With convenient proximity to restaurants, shopping, the airport, and the iconic Strip itself, this townhouse presents an unparalleled opportunity for both relaxation and entertainment in the heart of Las Vegas.
